      <title>越南将加大力度整顿黄金市场并打击走私</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/vietnam-to-step-up-actions-to-tame-gold-market-combat-smuggling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[稳定黄金市场对越南政府来说是一个紧迫的问题，走私者利用当地价格上涨的机会来贬值贵金属，导致汇率扭曲和越南盾疲软，从而损害经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/vietnam-to-step-up-actions-to-tame-gold-market-combat-smuggling</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 05:23:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
